---

<Layout 
  title={pageTitle}
  description={pageDescription}
  structuredDataType="WebPage"
  structuredData={{
    "@type": "Article",
    "headline": "Local SEO Checklist 2025",
    "author": {
      "@type": "Organization",
      "name": "Beach Bird Studios"
    },
    "publisher": {
      "@type": "Organization",
      "name": "Beach Bird Studios"
    }
  }}
>
  <Header />
  
  <Hero 
    headline="Local SEO <span class='text-yellow-400'>Checklist</span> for 2025"
    subheadline="50+ actionable items to improve your local search rankings and attract more customers"
    primaryCTA={{
      text: "Download Full Checklist",
      href: "/contact"
    }}
    secondaryCTA={{
      text: "Get SEO Help",
      href: "/services/seo-services"
    }}
  />

  <!-- Introduction Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          This comprehensive local SEO checklist contains over 50 proven tactics to improve your local search rankings. 
          Each item is actionable and designed specifically for small businesses competing in local markets.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
          Work through this checklist systematically to build a strong local SEO foundation. 
          Focus on the quick wins first, then tackle the more advanced strategies as your local presence grows.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-400 p-6 mb-8">
          <div class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <i data-lucide="target" class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-400"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-3">
              <p class="text-sm text-blue-700">
                <strong>Pro Tip:</strong> Don't try to tackle everything at once. Pick 3-5 items each week 
                and work through them consistently for best results.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Quick Wins -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-green-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Quick Wins (Start Here)</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          These high-impact actions can be completed quickly and often show results within days or weeks.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <FeatureGrid features={quickWins} />
      
      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-green-100 rounded-full">
          <i data-lucide="clock" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mr-2"></i>
          <span class="text-green-800 font-medium">Time Required: 2-4 hours total</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- On-Page SEO -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">On-Page SEO Optimization</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Optimize your website pages to help search engines understand your location and services.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <FeatureGrid features={onPageSEO} />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content Strategy -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-cream-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Local Content Strategy</h2>
