            </h3>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <label class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                <input type="checkbox" class="form-checkbox h-4 w-4 text-blue-600">
                <span class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Claim and verify your listing</span>
              </label>
              <label class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                <input type="checkbox" class="form-checkbox h-4 w-4 text-blue-600">
